name: Kuboo - A totally awesome safe virtual world for young kids.
blurb: The safest and most realistic virtual world for young kids. Parent approved and adored by kids. Amazing premiums ending this month.

rewards.reward: Buy a Brick. You know this one, just like at school, and in the spirit of creating a safe online world for kids, we will put your name on a virtual plaque or digital gratitude wall inside Kuboo as a small "Thank You" for getting behind us.

Sneak Peek. A Beta membership with no waiting! The World of Kuboo is almost complete, but with your help, we can let you look inside Kuboo and have the earliest updates on all new features. You can also give us ideas, feedback, and changes you would like to see in the game. One avatar and login per pledge. This will be limited to the first 7000 players. PC and Mac versions both available.

In addition to a free 3 month full access membership you will be given 2 invitations to give out to your friends. \u00a0You will be able to play together on the playground, inside your houses, and all types of other games!

This one is a big value package! \u00a0In addition to receiving a 6 months full access membership you will also be given 2,000 tokens along with 10 stars, which are much harder to earn. \u00a0This package carries a value of $72.99.

Charter Customer. This allows you to pre-purchase the game for a full year and create unlimited avatars for your child. Along with the awesome online experience and Charter Status, you will get 10000 coins and 25 stars...which is enough to last a long time. This package is estimated to be worth $182.25. We will also put a Charter Member insignia on your avatar, so everyone will know you were one of the earliest Kuboo players. PC and Mac versions both available. Play begins in October. Customized insignias will be ready within 60 days.

Early Bird Special! \u00a0You will get all of the same stuff that would come with a $100 pledge, but for $10 less because you are smart enough to sign up early. \u00a0Hurry and get them while they last!
You will be receiving the $100 package plus a picture signed by Kuboo.com spokesperson and Hollywood superstar Nick Cannon!\r\n* International shipping rates apply

This is for the humanitarian in everyone. \u00a0You will receive a 1 year full access membership to Kuboo.com, as well as a laptop donated in your name to a child in a children\u2019s hospital that is partnered with Safe Communications. \u00a0

Here is a once in a lifetime experience! \u00a0You will not only receive a 1 year full access membership, but the Hollywood VIP treatment. \u00a0You will be given tickets for you plus 3 to a show hosted by Kuboo.com spokesperson and Hollywood superstar Nick Cannon! \u00a0You will be flown out to the show, have a limo ride to and from the show IN ADDITION to a private meet and greet with Nick Cannon himself!\r\n* Does not include hotel accommodations
